high_descs: Go straight towards the counters ahead.
Pick up the knife on the counter to the right of the microwave.
Turn to the potato on the same countertop.
Slice the potato with the knife.
Turn to the microwave on the left.
Put the knife into the microwave.
Turn back to the sliced potato.
Pick up one potato slice.
Turn back to the microwave.
Use the microwave on the potato slice and retrieve it.
Look to the counter in front of the microwave.
Place the potato slice down in front of the microwave.

Turn around move towards the potato.
Cut the potato into slices.
Turn around and move towards the microwave in the slab.
Open the microwave, place the knife inside and close.
Turn around move towards the countertop.
Take a slice of the potato.
Turn around and move towards the microwave in the slab.
Open the oven, place the potato inside, close the oven, and take the potato out after cooking.

Place the potato slice on the countertop in front of the oven.

Pick up the knife that's next to the microwave.
Look to the right of the microwave where the potato is.
Slice the potato with the knife.
Look towards the microwave on the left.
Put the knife inside the microwave.
Look back towards the potato you just sliced.
Pick up a single potato slice.
Look back towards the microwave.
Use the microwave on the potato slice and pick it back up.
Look down at the counter the microwave is on.
Put the potato slice down in front of the microwave.
